this.attachCallbacksAndBindings();\n\n          if ($('body.is-ie.is-ie-lte-8').length === 0) this.animateScrollHeader();\n        },\n\n        animateScrollHeader: function animateScrollHeader() {\n setupHeaderAnimation() {\n            window.addEventListener('scroll', function(event) {\n              if(!didScroll) {\n                didScroll = true;\n                setTimeout(scrollPage, 220);\n              }\n            }, false);\n          }\n\n          function scrollPage() {\n            if (scrollY() >= changeHeaderOn) {\n              $header.addClass('scroll-header-shrink');\n              Theme.checkAndDismissOpenMenu();\n            } else {\n              $header.removeClass('scroll-header-shrink');\n              Theme.checkAndReinstateMenu();\n            }\n            didScroll = false;\n          }\n\n          function scrollY() {\n            return window.pageYOffset || docElem.scrollTop;\n          }\n\n          setupHeaderAnimation();\n        },\n\n        attachCallbacksAndBindings: function callbacksAndBindings() {\n          var hasTouch = $('html.touch').length;\n\n          // Register all applicable callbacks and bindings that should be trigegred upon theme init.\n          $(function() {\n            // Dismiss any open submenus on clicking anywhere else\n            $(document).on(hasTouch ? 'touchend' : 'click', function(e) {\n              if (!$(e.target).closest('.subnav-parent').hasClass('expanded')) {\n                Theme.closeOpenSubmenus();\n              }\n            });\n\n            // Make vertically stacked subnavs line up correctly\n            $('.nav .horizontal .subnav-parent > a').click(function() {\n                var $this = $(this),\n                    pWidth = parseInt($this.css('width')),\n                    $target = $this.siblings('.subnav.subnav--vertically-stacked'),\n                    tWidth, wDiff,\n                    pExpanded = $this.closest('.subnav-parent').hasClass('expanded');\n\n                var resetPos = function resetPos() {\n                  $target.css({ left: 0 });\n                }\n\n                if $('.subnav-parent.expanded').removeClass('expanded');\n        },\n\n        equaliseGrid: function equaliseGrid() {\n          var colSize, left, right, leftHeight, rightHeight,\n              $body = $('body'), $productImages = $('.prods .prod .prod__image-holder');\n\n          // scroll to bottom of page if having come from update basket\n          if (location.search.match('basket_updated')) {\n            $('body').scrollTop($(document).height()-$(window).height());\n          }\n\n          // identify grid column size in use\n          if ($body.hasClass('dsp-xs')) { colSize = 2; }\n          else if ($body.hasClass('dsp-sm'))  { colSize = 3; }\n          else if ($body.hasClass('dsp-md'))  { colSize = 4; }\n          else if ($body.hasClass('dsp-lg'))  { colSize = 6; }\n          else { colSize = 8; }\n\n          $productImages.height('auto');   // reset image cell heights so we can calculate accurately\n\n          // Group the products in batches of the known colSizes\n          // to find the tallest in the group and set that as the baseline height for the group\n          for (var i=0; i < $productImages.length; i+=colSize) {\n            var group = $productImages.slice(i, i+colSize),\n                tallestHeight = Theme.getHeightOfGroup(group);\n\n            if (tallestHeight > 30) {\n              group.height(tallestHeight); // do not perform sizing if height is unreasonable.\n            }\n          }\n        },\n\n        getHeightOfGroup: function getHeightOfGroup($group) {\n          var tallest = 0;\n          $group.each(function() {\n            var thisHeight = $(this).height();\n            if (thisHeight > tallest) tallest = thisHeight;\n          });\n          return tallest;\n        },\n\n        optimiseMainMenu: function optimiseMainMenu() {\n          // =>  Main navs\n          $('.is-nav-collapsible-item').each(function() {\n            var $this = $(this), links = $subnav.addClass('subnav--gridded subnav--is-fullwidth');\n            }\n          });\n        },\n\n        // determine available screen width & height\n          // Extra small devices (Phones) (<768px)\n          // Small devices (Tablets)   (≥768px)\n          // Medium devices (Desktops) (≥992px)\n          // Large devices (Desktops)  (≥1200px)\n          // extra Large devices (Desktops)  (≥1800px)\n        setDeviceDetails: function setDeviceDetails() {\n          var o, oOrig, dsp, dspOrig,\n              $body = $('body'),\n              h = $(window).height(),\n              w = $(window).width(),\n              dspClasses = 'dsp-xs dsp-sm dsp-md dsp-lg dsp-xlg',\n              orientClasses = 'dsp-portrait dsp-landscape';\n\n          // fetch some original data\n          dspOrig = $body.data('display-type');\n          oOrig   = $body.data('orientation');\n\n          $body.data('width', w).data('height', h); // attach the viewport dimensions to DOM\n\n          // determin screen display type\n          if (w < 768) { dsp = 'dsp-xs'; }\n          else if (w >= 768  && w < 992)  { dsp = 'dsp-sm'; }\n          else if (w >= 992  && w < 1200)  { dsp = 'dsp-md'; }\n          else if (w >= 1200 && w < 1800)  { dsp = 'dsp-lg'; }\n          else { dsp = 'dsp-xlg'; }\n\n          o = (w >= h) ? 'landscape' : 'portrait';   // determine screen orientation\n\n          // Reorganise grids if scrWidth changes more than XXpx since last dspType update\n          if (dspOrig === dsp) {\n            var xW = $body.data('uWidth') || 0,\n                wDiff = Math.abs(w - xW),\n                threshold = 0; // Increase threshhold if performance is an issue\n            if (wDiff > threshold) {\n              Theme.equaliseGrid();\n            }\n          }\n\n          // Check and set orientation when changed\n          if (oOrig !== o) {\n            $body.data('orientation', o).removeClass(orientClasses).addClass('dsp-'+o);  // tag DOM with new orientation;\n            setTimeout(function() {$(document).trigger('scr-orientation-changed');}, 50);\n          }\n\n          // check and set display type when changed\n          if (dspOrig !== dsp) {\n            $body\n              .data('display-type', dsp)  // tag the page with the relevant new type\n              .data('uHeight', h)         // height when dsp type was set\n              .data('uWidth', w);         // width when dsp type was set\n            $body.removeClass(dspClasses).addClass(dsp);\n            setTimeout(function() {$(document).trigger('scr-display-type-changed'); }, 50);\n          }\n        },\n\n        setFullScreenMenuHeight: function setFullScreenMenuHeight() {\n          var $el = $('.js-navbar-fullscreen'),\n              navHeight = $('.navbar > .navbar-header').height();\n              vHeight = $('body').data('height') - navHeight;\n          $el.css({ minHeight: vHeight, maxHeight: vHeight });\n        },\n\n        setProductHeightLimit: function setProductHeightLimit() {\n          var vHeight = $('body').data('height'),\n              navHeight = $('.navbar > .navbar-header').height(),\n              konstant = vHeight > 590 ? 20 : 10,\n              vDiff = vHeight -
